<p>
  <span class="nym">Gerbert</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German, Old Saxon</span> <i>gēr</i> 'spear' + <span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>beraht</i>, <span class="lang">Old Saxon</span> <i>berht</i> 'bright' from <span class="lang">Proto-Germanic</span> <i>*berhtaz</i>.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The birth name of an 11th C pope.</p>
</div>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>Cf. <a class="nym" href="Gerberta">Gerberta</a>.</p>
</div>
  


